All Classes

Class Description
Comparable
Used for comparing the two CRN numbers (the element and the object one) of the course in integer format.
CourseDBElement
CourseDBElement implements Comparable, and will consist of 5 separate attributes: the Course ID (a String), the CRN (an int), the number of credits (an int), the room number (a String), and the instructor name (a String).
CourseDBGUI  
CourseDBManager
CourseDBManager implements the CourseDBManagerInterface.
CourseDBManager_GFA_Test
This is the Good Faith Attempt test file for the CourseDBManager
CourseDBManager_STUDENT_Test
This is the Student test file for the CourseDBManager class which is being implemented from the CourseDBManagerInterface and using its methods of emphasis.
CourseDBManagerInterface  
CourseDBManagerTest
This is the test file for the CourseDBManager which is implemented from the CourseDBManagerInterface
CourseDBStructure
CourseDBStructure implements the CourseDBStructureInterface that is provided.
CourseDBStructureInterface
This is the interface to the Course Database Structure Class.
CourseDBStructureTest
This is the test file for the CourseDBManager which is implemented from the CourseDBManagerInterface
FXMainPane
This panel is the basic panel, inside which other panels are placed.
IOException
IOException class - throws an IOException whenever an input file cannot be read or you cannot get or retrieve a CDE due to it not existing in the CourseDataBase.
